{"tid":2000284,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"讀書時vs做嘢後去旅行習慣改變","createTime":"2020-05-03T18:15:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-23T16:40:18.000Z","uid":3560,"like":104,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"20e686c9553cc8e1572e1f32d87d4b4ab66369c6","tid":2000284,"uid":3560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T18:15:48.000Z","msg":"讀書時去旅行：<br />\n1. 鐘意大班人 / 同屋企人去<br />\n2. 一次過去勁多地方慌死蝕<br />\n3. 盡量撘通宵火車 / 巴士慳一晚住宿<br />\n<br />\n做嘢後去旅行：<br />\n1. 鐘意自己一個人去<br />\n2. 旅行是休息，慢慢行就夠，最緊要扮無wifi等老細同事搵你唔到<br />\n3. 通宵巴士不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 留喺hostel多晚都係三舊水"},{"pid":"28bfd5283382606767c54cee80029436b624da9c","tid":2000284,"uid":134149,"like":150,"dislike":0,"score":150,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T18:20:21.000Z","msg":"讀書時：有時間但無錢去<br />\n做野後：無時間亦無錢去<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8ce0b7cf5756fe93469dfee8566ff8b34a323b5","tid":2000284,"uid":287329,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T18:20:42.000Z","msg":"我唔好旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80e7d6bd7023c94e4e5b345defd889026a875b3e","tid":2000284,"uid":3560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T18:21:26.000Z","msg":"讀書可以唔瞓咁半夜出去玩，做嘢後要瞓飽先出門口"},{"pid":"6037aabf015c8a923447e996df046c0080540f07","tid":2000284,"uid":3560,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"a8ce0b7cf5756fe93469dfee8566ff8b34a323b5","tid":2000284,"uid":287329,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T18:20:42.000Z","msg":"我唔好旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T18:21:59.000Z","msg":"咁你入旅遊台做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90b8358d1fb19a4e06036233420d3adbb14c240e","tid":2000284,"uid":287329,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-