.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過會揀有bar嘅hostel <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84b3b0046dc333dfad172c8b28ac476f44aaa765","tid":2000284,"uid":158980,"like":48,"dislike":0,"score":48,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T19:26:20.000Z","msg":"學生時期：覺得窮遊鬥少錢去得好多地方好威<br />\n而家：最好間酒店 餐廳舒舒服服 成個旅程最好係有個環節係有得係沙灘 攤住飲啤酒 錢唔係冇上限 但最好起碼所有野正正常常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2acfb10117b213f63ad7ab7f4182571f5c6bc083","tid":2000284,"uid":80874,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T19:33:50.000Z","msg":"讀書時接受到住hostel share toilet <br />\n出左離做幾年野覺得獨立廁所係基本野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2089cd40000a2b450701897a52239b75bd8077a8","tid":2000284,"uid":71524,"like":6,"dislike":9,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T19:44:34.000Z","msg":"讀書：<br />\n1. 住既地方有咁平得咁平 訓床位都得<br />\n2. 同人夾錢租車揸<br />\n3. 影相用手機/無反<br />\n<br />\n做野野：<br />\n1. 一定要定獨立廁所 最好有埋浴缸 只要唔過800蚊一晚就照俾<br />\n2. 自己一個去台灣租機車 會寧願熱同曬 都想試下唔同野<br />\n3. 影相用菲林機"},{"pid":"00e2fedb91a9fc3172bd3d4ce9e3885d3aaebeb9","tid":2000284,"uid":213607,"like":38,"dislike":1,"score":37,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T19:48:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />讀書時已經覺得獨廁必須..."},{"pid":"1e273dd4c44c0cf23b7c58d665388b102289776c","tid":2000284,"uid":3560,"like":3,"dislike":8,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"00e2fedb91a9fc3172bd3d4ce9e3885d3aaebeb9","tid":2000284,"uid":213607,"like":38,"dislike":1,"score":37,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T19:48:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />讀書時已經覺得獨廁必須..."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T19:49:25.000Z","msg":"我到而家都仲覺得share廁無所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"344534b60bb3f3f54620d7f81635efd0e4cb410b","tid":2000284,"uid":213607,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1e273dd4c44c0cf23b7c58d665388b102289776c","tid":